## 2026-03-28 - ThemeManager coverage gap "auto-fill from source"
- Implemented per-token "Fill" button and bulk "Fill all" button in the ThemeManager coverage gaps view. Extended CoverageToken type to track `missingRef` (the first broken alias target), `fillValue`, and `fillType`. Coverage computation now finds missing refs via alias chain traversal and looks up fill values across all loaded sets. Single fill uses POST /api/tokens/:set/*, bulk fill uses POST /api/tokens/:set/batch with strategy "skip". De-duplicates by missingRef to avoid redundant writes. Shows fillable count in "Fill all" button. Per-token fill buttons appear on hover. Both show loading states and error handling.
